title: Dababy Interview and more
itunes:title: Dababy Interview and more
description:
Today on the show we had Da Baby call in to the show, where they spoke about his new album, proving people wrong, his mom giving his first condom and more. Also, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to lieutenant governor of Texas Dan Patrick for his comments on the Corona Virus and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
